# Web Lab Scanner

Session-aware web application lab scanner built in Python for DVWA, Juice Shop, and similar training targets.

## Features
- Internal crawling with scope controls
- Cookie and header-based authenticated scanning
- Security header analysis
- Cookie flag analysis
- CSRF token heuristics
- Reflected XSS indicator probing
- SQL error indicator probing
- JSON and HTML reporting

## Status
Milestone 1 scaffold is in progress.

## Usage

    web-lab-scanner scan http://127.0.0.1:3000

## Safety
Use only against systems you own or are explicitly authorized to test.
